{
    "name": "多方塊採礦機",
    "icon": "techguns:oredrill:4",
    "category": "ore_drills",
    "pages": [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "採礦機為多方塊結構的機器，本書之$(l:machine_mechanics)《機器特性》$(/l)也適用於此機器。採礦機共有五種不同的建造型式，也可轉九十度橫向建造，但都必須與礦叢相接。本書$(l:oredrills/ore_clusters#formulas)此處$(/l)有輸出及能量的計算公式說明。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "techguns:oredrill_0_frame",
            "recipe2": "techguns:oredrill_1_scaffold"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "techguns:oredrill_2_rod",
            "recipe2": "techguns:oredrill_3_engine"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "techguns:oredrill_4_controller",
            "text": "找到$(l:oredrills/ore_clusters)礦叢$(/l)後就可放上鑽軸開始建造採礦機。擺好方塊後對著控制器$(thing)點擊滑鼠右鍵$()以完成建造。"
        },
        {
